title: Acta Mathematica Sinica 1989-2006
description:
Acta Mathematica Sinica (1989, 1990, 1995, 1996, 2000-2006)
 English | PDF | 146 Mb


 Acta Mathematica Sinica, English Series is a monthly journal established by the Chinese Mathematical Society (Founded in 1985). The journal publishes significant research papers from all branches of pure and applied mathematics. It provides authoritative reviews of current developments in mathematical research. Contributions are invited from researchers all over the world.
